  <thing id="cDthComp" name="Unbreathing Companion" description="This functions as the druid&#146;s {i}animal companion{/i}, except the companion is treated as a magical beast and has the unbreathing subtype. The companion is calculated as if the death mage were a druid 2 levels lower than her true class level.\n\n{b}NOTE:{/b} On the minion&apos;s Classes tab, apply the {i}Unbreathing Magical Beast{/i} template as a &quot;class level&quot;." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Gain unbreathing animal companion." uniqueness="unique">
