  <thing id="cDthDeatMs" name="Death Mask" description="You can create a temporary fetish by painting symbols on your face and body. This takes one minute, and requires pigments and stains the death mage can gather at no cost. The temporary fetish lasts for one hour per class level. During this time, you do not have to hold your fetish to access its powers." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Access fetish powers without holding it." uniqueness="unique">
