  <thing id="cDthGhasTo" name="Ghast Touch" description="At 8th level, as a standard action, you can paralyze a target by touching it. This is a touch attack that forces living creatures to make a Fortitude save (DC 10 + &#189; your death mage level + your Charisma modifier). On a failed save, the target is paralyzed for one round per death mage level. At the end of each of its turns, the paralyzed target may make another fortitude save at a &#150;5 penalty to see if its paralysis ends early. You may use this power a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Charisma modifier." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Paralyze target for 1 round per Death Mage level.">
