  <thing id="cDthSumShd" name="Summon Shadow" description="At 8th level, you gain the ability to summon three shadows to serve you.  This acts as a {i}summon monster V{/i} spell, except it always summons three shadows, the shadows are of your alignment, and the effect has a duration of one minute per death mage level. You may use this ability once per day at 8th level, twice at 12th level, three times at 16th level and four times per day at 20th level. Beginning at 16th level, you may choose to have the shadows be greater shadows, if you wish." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Summon 3 shadows.">
