  <thing id="spDthAnUdS" name="Anti-Undead Shell" description="You bring into being a mobile, hemispherical energy field that prevents the entrance of most types of undead. Mindless undead (those with no Intelligence score) are automatically affected by this spell. Other undead receive a Will save when they first come into contact with an antiundead shell. On a failed save they are unable to enter the shell for its duration, on a successful save they ignore the spell. \n\nThis spell may only be used defensively, not aggressively. Forcing an abjuration barrier against creatures that spell keeps at bay collapses the barrier." compset="Spell" summary="10-ft.-radius field hedges out living creatures.">
